channel.title: Webfire
channel.description:
I have been working on this project in visual basic from scratch some time now and i am finnialy releaseing it for public use. It is a web browser similar to internet explorer but with greater speed and less lagg time. If you would like to download here is the link:[url=http://www.mediafire.com/?9178f5tz8qb7uhf]http://www.mediafire.com/?9178f5tz8qb7uhf[/url] and here is the verfication code needed to run the program: 253425342jjb636252 enjoy and i might release the source once im done with 2.0 If you wish for a better another virus scan try here: [url=http://www.virustotal.com/file-scan/report.html?id=0193ee96d01455a4e3db8297819732e21b7f6cc70ba8dee9433bf174c09147ec-1305473508]http://www.virustotal.com/file-scan/report.html?id=0193ee96d01455a4e3db8297819732e21b7f6cc70ba8dee9433bf174c09147ec-1305473508[/url]
Here are the features Of V.1: Forward Back Combo-box with history and current webpage address View source play music in background view how many links are in webpage set homepage home progress bar page properties print page print preview and chatbox comeing in next update
